          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夏侯惇 （同点绛唇） 马蹄奔忙，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将 （同点绛唇） 烟尘齐扫荡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐晃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "徐晃。"
        },
        {
          "character": "于禁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "于禁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "张辽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "张辽。"
        },
        {
          "character": "许褚",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "许褚。"
        },
        {
          "character": "乐进",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "乐进。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李典",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "李典。"
        },
        {
          "character": "夏侯渊",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夏侯渊。"
        },
        {
          "character": "夏侯惇",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夏侯惇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "于禁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "诸位将军请了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "于禁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "想我军，此次出征，剿灭河北袁绍，仗关羽英勇，斩了颜良、文丑，才得班师"
        },
        {
          "character": "于禁",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "许都。今日丞相升帐，吾等两厢伺候。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、四上手、荀彧、曹操同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "引子",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谋略压群雄，掌生杀，剿灭凶勇，壁垒森严，谁敢轻，定乾坤，狼烟齐扫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忆昔当年居孝廉，谋刺董卓起祸端。中牟县内得脱难，才得领兵掌大权！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老夫曹操。只因前者，河北袁绍，兴兵攻打白马坡，颜良、文丑被关羽刀劈落"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马。吾军齐唱凯歌，班师回朝。今日升帐理事。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众位将军、众将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吾军屡次凯歌，老夫奏知圣上，众军定有升赏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相提拔。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启禀丞相：今有汝南刘辟、龚都谋反，曹洪将军屡战不胜，难以抵敌，报与丞"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "相知道。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再探！"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "众将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相，探马报道，刘辟、龚都谋反，曹洪将军难以取胜，就该派吾等，前去帮"
        },
        {
          "character": "众将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "助。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "言得极是，容吾思之。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嗯喷。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闲观春秋孙武策，白马解围显英杰。赤兔喜走千里路，青龙爱饮上将血。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "闻得汝南谋反，曹洪难以对敌，不免进帐讨令，一来寻兄下落，二来报曹公之"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "恩待。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奸相枉将虚礼侍，岂知关羽不降曹。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相在上，关某参。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二将军少礼，请坐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢座。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二将军进帐，有何公论？"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "某闻汝南谋反，关某愿效犬马之劳，平复汝南。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二将军建立大功，未曾重酬，岂可复劳征讨！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "丞相不知，关羽久闲，必生病矣！"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此就复劳将军前往。于禁、乐进以为副将，余下将士随营调遣。统领五万人"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "马，平复汝南回来，老夫率领大小三军，亲自出城，迎接十里之外。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得令呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "云长接令暗自笑，"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "曹公真个有韬略："
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "上马金下马银奉敬英豪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "关羽",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一来报效二来寻故交。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（关羽下，众将同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "荀彧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊？丞相，那云长素有归刘之心，倘知消息必去矣。丞相何用云长出征？丞相"
        },
        {
          "character": "荀彧",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "详查。"
        },
        {
          "character": "曹操",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今次取功，吾不复教云长临敌，以隐他去之心。掩门！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
